00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,230
saya dah buat keputusan
pergi ke Alam Termulia.

492
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:05,000
Saya takkan kembali ke Alam Dewa

493
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,640
